'''Anfa''' neɣ '''Taddart Tumlilt''' (s [[Tafrensist|Tefṛansist]] d tulayin tiyaḍ: "Casablanca", s tutlayt [[Taɛṛabt]]: "الدار البيضاء") d iɣṛem ameqqṛan akk di tmurt en [[Lmerruk]]. Zeddɣen deg-s 5 melyun n yimdanen. Anfa d-iɣṛem ameqqran akk deg [[Tmazɣa]] akked Lezzayer Tamanaɣt.

Tella deg '''Anfa''' yiwet tmezgida tameqqṛant isem ines Timezgida Ḥasan Wis 2.

== Tarakalt ==
anfa yella deg tesga en Anfa-Ẓeṭṭaṭ di tmurt en [[Lmerruk]].

